        "created_at": "2018-01-20T05:56:34.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=2899463\"><strong>1937 Domaine Armand Naulot Clos Vougeot</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Nuits, Clos Vougeot Grand Cru (1/18/2018)</em><br>\nA wonderful, aged bottle of Burgundy with plenty of life and vigor. The nose has complex aromatics of seaweed, compost, leather, spice and a suggestion of dark fruits. It is intense and strong in the mouth with good detail and freshness. It builds through the palate and finishes with good cut. There are all sorts of savoury nuances once the wine is swallowed and it is a cerebral wine that titillates the senses.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
